languages.text: Allows Wrath Starfighters to be launched through {g|Encyclopedia:TorpedoLaunchersSpace}torpedo tubes{/g}. A Wrath Starfighters wing consists of 4 attack crafts, each of them equipped with a heavy laser turret. ! Up to 2 wings of Wrath Starfighters can be active at a time.

traits.locale_text: Allows to launch wing of Wrath Starfighters through torpedo ports. Wing consist of 4 crafts equipped with heavy laser turrets. ! Can't have more than 2 wings active at once.

languages.text: 可以通过{g|Encyclopedia:TorpedoLaunchersSpace}鱼雷发射管{/g}发射怒焰星际战斗机联队。 怒焰星际战斗机联队由4架战斗机组成，每架战斗机都配备一门重型激光炮台。 ！同一时间可以派遣两支怒焰星际战斗机联队。
